name: livingroom_1
description:
livingroom is a micro-collection of 3 pieces made before "dist_room" using some node editing in a primitive render from a 3d modeling I've made. the simple house layout get alive by itself just having some color effects. 
the frames on the "dist_room" wall - clearly visible at dist_room_1 - are prints of this livingroom animation.
